snippet.title: JW Montoya
snippet.description:
My name is JW Montoya. I am 27 years old and Live in Augusta, Georgia. I have been making YouTube videos since 2010, but I started taking it seriously in 2016. I started this channel while I was in college and working at my part time job. After graduating college and working at my full time job, I had to figure out a way to still make YouTube videos. In October of 2020, I was able to quit my full time job and focus 100 percent on YouTube and my business, https://jwmotorsportsco.com.

On this channel, I will be helping you with reviews, 'how to' videos, and anything truck stuff. My passion doe lie on diesel trucks so there may be more diesel content, but I love all trucks.

Upload Schedule:
Tuesday, Thursday, and Saturday (some time on Sunday)
